  <steps>
    <step order="1">Add integration smoke test file under daily-briefing-components</step>
    <step order="2">Mock notificationService.fetchNotifications to return 8 items across 3 categories (e.g., 3 email, 3 document, 2 event)</step>
    <step order="3">Mock /narrate response with `totalNotificationCount: 8` and matching channelNarratives</step>
    <step order="4">Render DailyBriefingApp with mocked services</step>
    <step order="5">Assert header text shows count `8` (or whatever the TL;DR component renders for totalNotificationCount)</step>
    <step order="6">Assert ActivityNotesSection renders exactly 8 NarrativeBullet items</step>
    <step order="7">Add negative-path test: if mocked /narrate returns mismatched count (e.g., 5), test FAILS with clear message — this confirms the test would catch a regression</step>
    <step order="8">Run `npm test`; ensure pass</step>
    <step order="9">Update TASK-INDEX.md ✅</step>
    <step order="10">Document deviations in notes/</step>
  </steps>
